<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HKN-SHARKS-NOTES-TEX </SLUG>
 
(For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TRACEY MYERS AND JEFF CAPLAN 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
