<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-MEDIA-TECH-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
DAMMING THE FLOW OF FREE INFORMATION 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 By FELICITY BARRINGER   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
