have built 20 space shuttles out of what washed up on this very
beach! You couldn't find a way to get us home?
</P>
<P>
   SKIPPER: But, Little Buddy, I __
</P>
<P>
   GILLIGAN: Shut your snackhole, Fatty, I'm not done yet. To think
of the years I've wasted putting up with your bullying, your
insults, your impotent, passive-aggressive rage. ... Don't blame me
for your low self-esteem, Roundboy, it's not my fault you've been
living on nothing but fruit and fish since 1964 but haven't lost an
ounce! And don't think I don't feel your eyes on me at night in the
hut. ...
</P>
<P>
   SKIPPER: Aw, Gilligan. (A stone the size of a fist whizzes past
his head.) Yikes! (He flees.)
</P>
<P>
   As the camera CRANES UP we see GILLIGAN, naked now in the dying
light of the fire, grotesque and mud-covered, roasting the bones of
a small animal and talking to himself.
</P>
<P>
   ANNOUNCER: Join us again next week when the former cast of
``Fantasy Island'' plays ``Celebrity Survivor'' here on CBS! FADE
TO BLACK.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
