<P>
   MEDAL-WORTHY ACTING JOB
</P>
<P>
   You may not be an Olympic athlete, but you can play one on TV!
Children's publisher Scholastic Inc. wants your teacher to submit
video clips of your classmates dressed as their favorite athletes,
playing Olympic sports, greeting viewers or announcing at the
Olympics. Fifty clips will be chosen to be played on MSNBC during
the Summer Olympics in Australia. See
www.Scholastic.com/Olympicgames for rules. Deadline is June 23.
</P>
