 &HT;    Now, at 57, Ali rarely speaks in public. When he does, his words
are slurred. Only his hands shake more than his head. He's the
equivalent of a massive teddy bear. So many of those who absolutely
couldn't stand Ali in the past, can't get enough of him now. In
