<HEADLINE>
YIPPEE! FINALLY, THE CANDIDATES TALK ABOUT FOREIGN POLICY  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 1,000-word material from The New York
