   0509 COLOR WEATHER -- 3 x 4 1/4 -- National forecast map in
color.
</P>
<P>
   0509 B&AMP;W WEATHER -- 3 x 4 1/4 -- National forecast map.
</P>
<P>
   0509 MOON PHASES -- 1 x 5/8 -- The phases of the moon.
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
