<P>
   WORKOUT-PILATES &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ You've got something in common with Madonna and Monica
if you hope to become more flexible and strong by using the Pilates
exercise method. Once the almost exclusive restorative of
professional dancers, it's becoming popular with many who seek a
low-impact but intense workout. By CAROLYN POIROT. Story will move
in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   STAPLES-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ My daughter wanted to know if it was true that Whitney
Houston is addicted to drugs. I told her I didn't know, but I hope
not. Remembering the look of concern on her face as she asked the
question, it occurred to me how involved we can become in the lives
of people we only read about in newspaper headlines, see on
television and in the movies, or in magazine photographs. By GRACIE
BONDS STAPLES. Story has moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
