   UNDATED _ A query for the computer guy: ``Dear Dr. Bombay: Do
you think if the Justice Department gets its way and breaks up
Microsoft into separate companies, we'll have another fiasco like
when they broke up Ma Bell? Remember when you could call one number
for service and get help? Now you don't know who or where to call
for your telephone service.'' By DR. EMILIO BOMBAY. Story has moved
in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
